Vulnerability Issues.Details: Versions of lodash lower than 4.17.12 are vulnerable to Prototype Pollution. The function defaultsDeep could be tricked into adding or modifying properties of Object.prototype using a constructor payload.
Vulnerability Issues.Remediation Advice: This vulnerability exists in a transitive dependency. It can be upgraded by adding the project as a direct dependency. Add lodash-es@4.17.14 as a direct dependency
